737
01:03:09,440 --> 01:03:13,399
- "Can I fluff your pillows?"
- I got flustered, I panicked.

738
01:03:13,560 --> 01:03:16,120
You have to help me,
it was working.

739
01:03:16,280 --> 01:03:18,794
