740
01:03:19,800 --> 01:03:24,112
She wants somebody who looks like me
and talks like you.

741
01:03:35,000 --> 01:03:36,797
No, come here.

742
01:03:37,800 --> 01:03:40,314
Do not make me do it.

743
01:03:40,480 --> 01:03:43,756
Stand under the window,
I will be out of sight.

744
01:03:43,920 --> 01:03:47,959
- I whisper to you what to say.
- Wait, what if she hears you?

745
01:03:48,120 --> 01:03:50,236
Just call her.

746
01:03:50,720 --> 01:03:52,950
Roxanne?

747
01:03:59,720 --> 01:04:01,517
Go easy for once!

748
01:04:01,680 --> 01:04:04,513
Goddamn it, what are you doing?

749
