I am sorry, hold on.

750
01:04:06,480 --> 01:04:10,439
- Listen to me, I have a lot to say.
- Go away!

751
01:04:10,600 --> 01:04:14,957
- I just want to tell you that...
- That I am really built?

752
01:04:15,120 --> 01:04:19,557
- No, nothing like that.
- Tell her you were an idiot.

753
01:04:19,720 --> 01:04:22,075
I was an idiot, Roxanne.

754
01:04:22,240 --> 01:04:23,753
Wait, come here!

755
01:04:25,240 --> 01:04:27,276
