788
01:06:35,280 --> 01:06:40,308
I can be myself, Roxanne.
Oh God, your name is like a knife.

789
01:06:40,480 --> 01:06:42,357
Stand where I can see you.

790
01:06:42,520 --> 01:06:45,830
- No!
- Why?

791
01:06:46,920 --> 01:06:51,789
Only my voice, you do not need
to see me, just listen to me.

792
01:06:51,960 --> 01:06:57,034
