Did what I wrote touch you?

793
01:06:58,040 --> 01:06:59,996
It did.

794
01:07:01,440 --> 01:07:03,317
It was eloquent.

795
01:07:03,480 --> 01:07:07,314
No, not eloquent, just honest.

796
01:07:11,280 --> 01:07:17,037
I am in orbit around you,
I am suspended weightless over you -

797
01:07:17,200 --> 01:07:20,556
- like the blue man in the Chagall, -

798
01:07:22,400 --> 01:07:25,551
- hanging over you in a delirious kiss.

799
01:07:27,800 --> 01:07:31,793
Yesterday, on the street...
I swore I heard your name.

800
01:07:34,000 --> 01:07:40,109
I turned and there was nobody there.
Just five birds rising off the ground -

801
01:07:40,280 --> 01:07:44,990
- and when their wings hit the air,
I heard your name again.

802
01:07:45,160 --> 01:07:51,156
Just for that second I was one of them,
pounding out your name: Roxanne.

803
01:07:51,320 --> 01:07:57,236
Roxanne. A word of two syllables
locked inside my head.

804
01:07:59,440 --> 01:08:05,515
You see... I am...
and I will always be -

805
01:08:07,680 --> 01:08:10,672
- the one who loved you
without limits.

806
01:08:10,840 --> 01:08:14,628
What are you talking about?
It is too much.

807
01:08:14,800 --> 01:08:18,190
- Go on.
- It is working, go on.

808
01:08:22,200 --> 01:08:28,514
This is my whole life right now.
Standing here talking to you like this.

809
01:08:28,680 --> 01:08:32,389
Saying things I wanted to say,
but could not.

810
01:08:32,560 --> 01:08:35,120
Why could you not talk to me?

811
01:08:35,280 --> 01:08:38,556
I was afraid you would laugh at me.

812
01:08:38,720 --> 01:08:42,633
- That is silly.
- No, not if you knew.

813
01:08:42,800 --> 01:08:47,078
When you are reaching for a star,
there is a long way to fall.

814
01:08:47,240 --> 01:08:50,596
