815
01:08:50,760 --> 01:08:55,276
Now I feel sorry for people for whom
it never comes.

816
01:08:56,800 --> 01:09:02,238
I love you. I have breathed you in
and I am suffocating.

817
01:09:03,240 --> 01:09:08,917
I am crazy, I cannot go on.
This is all too much.

818
01:09:09,080 --> 01:09:15,394
- I am starting to feel a little dizzy.
- I am starting to feel a little drunk.

819
01:09:15,560 --> 01:09:19,997
Because I have
made you tremble up there, have I not?

820
01:09:21,680 --> 01:09:23,910
Like a leaf on a tree.

821
01:09:24,080 --> 01:09:27,595
- I want to make love to you.
